# ─────────────────────────────────────────────
# Bybit API Keys
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────
# Get your keys at: https://www.bybit.com/app/user/api-management
#
# IMPORTANT: When creating your API key on Bybit:
#   1. Go to Account & Security > API Management
#   2. Click "Create New Key"
#   3. Choose "System-generated API Keys"
#   4. Permissions needed: "Read-Write" for Trade
#   5. Restrict to your IP address for security
#   6. For paper trading only, "Read" permission is enough
#
EXCHANGE_API_KEY=your_bybit_api_key_here
EXCHANGE_API_SECRET=your_bybit_api_secret_here
